articles.title: Five key takeaways from Trump’s week in Asia - NPR
articles.description: President Trump is back in Washington after spending a week in Asia. He attended the ASEAN summit in Kuala Lumpur, addressed U.S. troops in Japan and met with China's President Xi Jinping in South Korea.
